---------------------------------------------------------

balances[attacker] = 0

---------------------------------------------------------

require() fails.

---------------------------------------------------------

Reentrancy blocked naturally.

=========================================================
WHY SAFE ORDERING WORKS
=========================================================

Attacker sees:
UPDATED state.

---------------------------------------------------------

Temporary inconsistent state
never exposed.

=========================================================
IMPORTANT SECURITY PRINCIPLE
=========================================================

Update internal accounting
BEFORE external interaction.

=========================================================
CEI PATTERN
=========================================================

---------------------------------------------------------
1. CHECKS
---------------------------------------------------------

Validate conditions.

---------------------------------------------------------
2. EFFECTS
---------------------------------------------------------

Update storage.

---------------------------------------------------------
3. INTERACTIONS
---------------------------------------------------------

External calls LAST.

=========================================================
REMIX TESTING
=========================================================

STEP 1:
Deploy SafeBank

---------------------------------------------------------

STEP 2:
Deposit several ETH

---------------------------------------------------------

